Event Season History

Source: R/scoutR.R
event_season_history.Rd

Given an event code, this function returns all a dataframe with all the robot-level results of teams registered for a particular event.

Usage

event_season_history(event_code, fields = NULL, manual_teams = NULL)

Arguments

event_code

TBA-legal event code (ex. "2024paca")

fields

optional, robot fields you want to retrieve. If NULL, uses `id_robot_fields()` to get individual robot-level fields automatically.

manual_teams

(int) additional teams to manually add to the team list

Details

Checks for match duplication, which will stop execution if TRUE.

Examples

gpr24 <- event_season_history("2024paca")
